    "description": "<strong>Welcome to Borefest. The most boring game ever made.</strong><br><br>Do you hate having fun? Enjoy torturing yourself with lackluster puzzles, dialogue that tries WAY too hard to be funny, and/or graphics &quot;drawn&quot; by someone who can't draw? Well, you've come to the right place...<br><br>Borefest is the most boring game in the world, and in it, you'll be waiting in line at the post office, answering questions during a workplace safety meeting, serving customers during a VERY slow shift - basically, all the most tedious things in life are in this game...<br><br>Only those with brave enough souls and the most tenacious spirits can endure:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- 6 &quot;mini&quot;games that each span upwards of 30 minutes</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- An unlockable 'hard mode' that makes those &quot;mini&quot;games EVEN worse</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- A soundtrack comprised of royalty-free 'Kevin Macleod' music</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- Extremely long loading screens</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- Dull gameplay mechanics that include: waiting around and pressing one button, QTE's, quizzes.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>- Unskippable dialogue</li></ul><br>Don't buy this game if you enjoy having fun - if you want to experience the most boring things life has to offer and try to conquer them in an extremely anti-climactic fashion, this &quot;game&quot; is for you!<br><br><i>You'll have the life sucked out of you as you visit: the post office, a fast food restaurant, the A&amp;E waiting room...</i><br><br><i>You'll meet moderately humorous characters such as: a creepy clown, your boring boss, an obsessive stamp collector...</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404190/extras/9a3f79261136caa5978659ef078e5cdc.poster.avif?t=1686425592\" width=615 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404190/extras/9a3f79261136caa5978659ef078e5cdc.webm?t=1686425592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>...Honestly, just go play something else.",
